data.description: Welcome to this timeless mid-century modern jewel! Located in popular Madison Park, this home is minutes from many eateries, shopping and the light rail. This home features a sun filled open great room, dining area and kitchen.  The kitchen has a gas range, generous cabinetry, a tile floor and large island. There are original hardwoods floors throughout and tile in the kitchen and bath. Two hall closets provide nice storage areas. A unique  planked ceiling with beams is present throughout the home, offering authentic character from its 1950's era. The kitchen opens to a large, flat backyard and large patio area, a great space for outside dining and entertaining.  This home is move-in ready and close to Southend, lower Southend, Southpark Mall and convenient to the airport. Don't miss this lovely gem!
